{"tid":1196533,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"據我理解 中胡椒噴霧 應該使用食油或者全脂牛奶沖洗","createTime":"2019-06-09T20:43:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-10T13:50:14.000Z","uid":30791,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"3c9f66571bd7e6bef47a1623680cc3e578c7ed9d","tid":1196533,"uid":30791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T20:43:57.000Z","msg":"根據我中學學既化學 由於辣椒素係脂溶性的<br />\n所以應該用非極性溶劑 而唔係水黎沖洗<br />\n<br />\n考慮到溶劑對皮膚影響<br />\n用食油，全脂牛奶 沖洗應該比較安全<br />\n<br />\n讀化學既 或者試過既 有無補充?"},{"pid":"68dc5b898be81ac9c42420375168c7896781e8b0","tid":1196533,"uid":30791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T20:45:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71d0ef43e5cefd0c7a057ac980fe9fe69a02fc89","tid":1196533,"uid":142707,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3c9f66571bd7e6bef47a1623680cc3e578c7ed9d","tid":1196533,"uid":30791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T20:43:57.000Z","msg":"根據我中學學既化學 由於辣椒素係脂溶性的<br />\n所以應該用非極性溶劑 而唔係水黎沖洗<br />\n<br />\n考慮到溶劑對皮膚影響<br />\n用食油，全脂牛奶 沖洗應該比較安全<br />\n<br />\n讀化學既 或者試過既 有無補充?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T20:51:17.000Z","msg":"食油洗眼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9cc004abbbd2dec6a11da7251c1f03748b51b809","tid":1196533,"uid":225739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T20:51:36.000Z","msg":"胡椒噴霧噴霧唔一定係辣椒素,又機會係其他刺激性有機物質"},{"pid":"1c5dd2582deb0e75324bd8f779af582717fbc753","tid":1196533,"uid":225739,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T20:56:10.000Z","msg":"胡椒噴霧急救點子:<br />\n<br />\n1. 不要用水沖。<br />\n2. 用吸收物科，例如乾紙巾，輕按沾了胡椒噴霧的部位，吸走此有害化學物質。<br />\n3. 不要使勁抹，因此舉會擴大受影響的皮膚範圍，亦可能增加皮膚的吸收，令不適更持久。<br />\n4. 每處理一個部位，便換上一塊未用過的紙巾，以免由於重複使用而把胡椒噴霧從一個位置，帶到另一位置。<br />\n5. 眼睛的處理亦是一樣。不要用水沖，先用乾紙巾吸收眼睛及周圍的胡椒噴霧。每隻眼睛‭ 用一塊或多塊紙巾，勿讓眼睛反覆接觸帶有胡椒噴霧的紙巾。<br />\n6. 眼睛分泌大量淚水，有助把刺激物質沖出眼睛之外。反而用水直接沖洗眼睛，有可能把頭髮、面額的刺激物質沖進眼睛。<br />\n<br />\n來源:<a href=\"http://hkjam.com/?p=5023\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkjam.com%2F%3Fp%3D5023&d=OwzbFhxxS8LWxL2ugy7iTByAur%2Bbp9MVyOkMM5%2FMxDY%3D&h=31a4932a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hkjam.com/?p=5023</a>"},{"pid":"14ceecd3a6f9310304e708d3338fd154897b0ef1","tid":1196533,"uid":30791,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9cc004abbbd2dec6a11da7251c1f03748b51b809","tid":1196533,"uid":225739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T20:51:36.000Z","msg":"胡椒噴霧噴霧唔一定係辣椒素,又機會係其他刺激性有機物質"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T20:58:14.000Z","msg":"唔一定係辣椒素 但係一般物質唔係水溶性就係脂溶性<br />\n水洗唔得就應該係脂溶性<br />\n或者係當中同時有水溶性及脂溶性物質"},{"pid":"82186d3c14837db1364d780781bbb4c0929232fc","tid":1196533,"uid":30791,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T21:03:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4f11f6a71539ae2e6c0a9a838f61f2fb9264092","tid":1196533,"uid":30791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T21:14:09.000Z","msg":"如果有人中招 不妨一試 然後話比大家聽效果如何"},{"pid":"f7f5b5ddcb081ae7298263066219c5ac0c978322","tid":1196533,"uid":50835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T21:15:07.000Z","msg":"［6.10-6.12］三日集中行動<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1196520\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1196520</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gDekzFq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgDekzFq.png&h=531a96a4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ab7615457aae4abe5f7ae972b5cd67126ce2cfeb","tid":1196533,"uid":30791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T21:19:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"715471f81c4274dda64058637cc6837579220b00","tid":1196533,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d4f11f6a71539a